name: Leeroy
text:
Don't stick to the plan. Stick to this card back.

name: Faelin
text: Though his voyage was a pricy one, no sunk cost was too great for him. Earnable after purchasing the Voyage to the Sunken City Tavern Pass.

name: Self-Made
text:

name: Violet Hold
text:

name: Submarine
text: It's about time we go and see what waits for us under the sea! Earnable on the Voyage to the Sunken City Reward Track.
